  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This primary purpose of this study is to estimate the maximum tolerated dose (MTD) and/or
      recommended dose for expansion (RDE) and preferred dosing schedule of LJM716 given by IV
      infusion in adult patients with squamous cell carcinoma of head and neck, or esophagus, or
      HER2 overexpressing metastatic breast cancer or gastric cancer
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
